Lab8a8 Fancy Word
Description
Read in one word at a time from the file and output the word as an hourglass.

Pass the matching test - see below.

Algorithm Help:
for(int i = 0; i < word.length(); i++) {
  mat[0][i] = word.substring(i , i+1);
  //3 more statements
  //like the one I gave you
}

Sample Input
6
HELLO
CAT
A
DOGHOUSE
ONE
IT

